### Create RxDB Database with Dexie Cloud Sync

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Creates an RxDB database instance utilizing the Dexie RxStorage that has been configured with the Dexie Cloud addon. This enables automatic synchronization with a Dexie Cloud backend.

```javascript
const db = await createRxDatabase({
  name: 'mydb',
  storage
});
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Dexie RxStorage with Dexie Cloud Addon

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Configures the Dexie RxStorage to include the Dexie Cloud addon and sets up the necessary cloud configuration, including the database URL and authentication requirements. The `onCreate` hook is used to configure Dexie Cloud when a new database instance is created.

```javascript
const storage = getRxStorageDexie({
  addons: [dexieCloud],
  /*   * Whenever a new dexie database instance is created,   * this method will be called.   */
  async onCreate(dexieDatabase, dexieDatabaseName) {
    await dexieDatabase.cloud.configure({
        databaseUrl: "https://<yourdatabase>.dexie.cloud",
        requireAuth: true // optional
    });
  }
});
```

