### Install Dexie Cloud Addon for RxDB

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Installs the 'dexie-cloud-addon' package, which is required for enabling synchronization between RxDB and Dexie Cloud.

```bash
npm install dexie-cloud-addon
```

